version_description:
- Improved visibility of peak and gain displays
- Peak/gain display can now be changed in height
- Added explicit mono input, stereo output channel configuration

- Stability and efficiency improvements
- User-interface style redesign and improvements
- Peak, limiter gain, and loudness information now shown simultaneously
- New high-frequency saturation and auto saturation input modeller modes
- AU and AUv3 now save full plugin state including all programs in host
- Improved tooltips (long press to show)
- Updated iOS icon
Improved UI rendering for tiny form factors (e.g. scaled UI in AUM)
